The TKE workstation has one 1000BASE-T Ethernet port, and supports connectivity to an Ethernet local area network (LAN). Up to 10 features combined (0057/0058) can be ordered per IBM z16 A02 and IBM z16 AGZ. 0157 TKE Table Top Keyboard/Monitor/Mouse A table top monitor with a US English language keyboard. There is a touchpad for pointing, and a country-specific power cord. 0057 TKE rack-mounted workstation The rack-mounted version of the TKE, which needs a customer-provided standard 19-inch rack. It features a 1u TKE unit and an (optional) 1u console tray (screen, keyboard, and pointing device). When smart card readers are used, another customer-provided tray is needed.
